{"tid":334491,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"想尋返個失聯咗嘅巴打，有跑開步，鐘意短髮囡。","createTime":"2017-07-24T17:35:47.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-25T01:05:16.000Z","uid":52580,"like":3,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c0842cc8138afed87531f369659e9354173c578d","tid":334491,"uid":52580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T17:35:47.000Z","msg":"事源係咁嘅，早幾個月失戀，喺連登誤打誤撞咁認識咗一位巴打。多謝佢喺我最難過嘅時期不厭其煩咁喺tg 每晚十二至二同我閒聊吓大家嘅人生。聽我呻吓，教吓我人生道理。<br />\n<br />\n我記得你大概三十幾歲，份人好風趣亦都自認風趣，有跑步習慣，唔鐘意女仔長頭髮，成日叫我諗吓用手藝做吓小生意。三月話想睇黎明但無fd想去，有時會同同事啤啤佢。同我分享過感情事，仲話將ex嘅野收咗喺床底唔敢回望。 <br />\n<br />\n唔知搵唔搵得返呢個人，想知你而家生活成點。<br />\n印象中你個tg名係天空乜乜乜。<br />\n如果你認得我嘅，話我知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  唔該哂！"},{"pid":"6853496eb5ce5583acd4a2097918b92b1af499eb","tid":334491,"uid":21423,"like":3,"dislike":10,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T17:38:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1e26ed6c438cfa1a43ca1735c5d4ebc3717fa73f","tid":334491,"uid":52580,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T17:41:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">鐘意<span style=\"color: red;\">✗ <strong>鍾意</strong></span><br />\n囡<span style=\"color: red;\">✗ <strong>女（囡讀音南）</strong></span><br />\n野<span style=\"color: red;\">✗ <strong>嘢</strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imag.cx/XpIZI.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imag.cx%2FXpIZI.png&h=bedc9135&s={SIZE}\" /></span></blockquote><br />\n我明明已經好小心<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b1c3323f7700396a977b116d748020b4055d895","tid":334491,"uid":8028,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T18:49:23.000Z","msg":"咪理樓上條友 成日捉錯字 煩到嘔"},{"pid":"ba1f89233e1d22873604fc667587985ab3e4f345","tid":334491,"uid":52580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T19:39:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咪理樓上條友 成日捉錯字 煩到嘔</blockquote><br />\n睇嚟我都係尋唔到呢個爸打<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji